                        Get Started Now
                    </button>
                    <button class="cta-secondary px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-all w-full sm:w-auto">
                        View Packages
